* The Czech Republic has an embassy in Minsk.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.mzv.cz/minsk  Czech embassy in Minsk (in Czech and Belarussian only)]&lt;/ref&gt;
* Both countries are full members of the [[Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe]].
