In 2009 Belgium has 20 major media companies [[Concentration of media ownership|active in numerous telecommunications media subsectors]].&lt;ref&gt;Vlaamse Regulator voor de Media, Mediaconcentratie in Vlaanderen rapport 2009, Vlaamse overheid, Brussel, 2009&lt;/ref&gt; These are:

